'''Pamir University''' ({{lang-ps|د پامیر پوهنتون}}) is a private higher education institute which was officially inaugurated on April 24, 2011 in the city of [[Khost]], [[Khost Province]], southeastern [[Afghanistan]].<ref>[http://bakhtarnews.com.af/en/index.php?news=4934 Afghanistan Bakhtar News Agency] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724234839/http://bakhtarnews.com.af/en/index.php?news=4934 |date=2011-07-24 }}</ref>
Pamir University has three faculties: [[computer science]], [[language]] and [[literature]], and [[economics]].<ref>http://www.goodafghannews.com/2011/04/24/private-higher-education-institute-opens-in-khost-2-new-school-buildings-to-be-built-in-kapisa/</ref>
